ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 278, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 278 in order to (1) declare the 2024 interface fire that occurred in Jasper, Alberta, to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness to provide financial assistance to the Province.
